TOP LEVEL
A function that receives number of successful deliveries and calculates the rider's wage for the day

STEP-WISE REFINEMENT
declare basepay and initialise to 5000
declare amount per parcel and initialise to 0
if successful deliveries is greater than or equal to 70%, amount per parcel equals 500
else if successful deliveries is greater than or equal to 60%, amount per parcel equals 250
else if successful deliveries is greater than or equal to 50%, amount per parcel equals 200
else amount per parcel equals 160

return (deliveries multiplied by amount per parcel) plus the base pay

